</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-61_ pf-text-1">Effective pain management strategies and symptom control to enhance comfort and quality of life.

















































</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-63_ pf-text-1">Addressing psychological and existential concerns through compassionate listening and support.



















































